# Playwright Agent — Navigation Hints
# Schema: 2.0 | Colony: {{colony_name}}
# Load this file at the start of every Planner phase before generating navigation steps.

## Format

Each entry is keyed by hostname. All fields are optional — omit any field to fall back to defaults.

```json
{
  "{{hostname}}": {
    "wait_after_navigate_ms": 1500,
    "search_selector": "{{css_or_aria_selector}}",
    "result_selector": "{{css_or_aria_selector}}",
    "submit_selector": "{{css_or_aria_selector}}",
    "notes": "{{human_readable_note}}"
  }
}
```

## Active Hints

```json
{}
```

## How EarnedConstraints Add Entries

When the Reflector issues a navigation EarnedConstraint, it appends to this file:

```json
{
  "{{hostname}}": {
    "wait_after_navigate_ms": 3000,
    "search_selector": "{{corrected_selector}}",
    "notes": "EC-NAV-{{id}}: Auto-added after {{failure_count}} consecutive failures on {{date}}"
  }
}
```

The Planner reads this file before generating navigation steps in every subsequent cycle.

## Default Values (when no hint exists)

- `wait_after_navigate_ms`: 1500
- `search_selector`: auto-detect from accessibility tree (role=searchbox or input[type=search])
- `result_selector`: auto-detect from accessibility tree
- `submit_selector`: auto-detect (role=button name~=/search|submit|go/i)
